  m_text: 'Dear

    It''s your firt assigment as newly promoted Warden. From now
    your on your own. We in headquaters have high hopes for you.

    Your quest
    is to check situation in this place. Far from capital and other highly populated
    regions. You should start form the village Fishville. '
